What is tm-gnus?
****************

tm-gnus is a MIME extender for GNUS using tm.

Note: tm-gnus is for only GNUS. Please use gnus-mime for Gnus.
      (*Note (gnus-mime_en.info)::)

tm-gnus decodes RFC 1522 MIME encoded-word in summary buffer and article
buffer, and adds a command to preview MIME message using tm-view in
summary mode.

In GNUS 3.15 or later and Gnus, tm-gnus can display MIME preview buffer
instead of article buffer. It is useful for heavy MIME user.




