Composing MIME message
**********************

If using mime-setup (*Note (tm_en.info)Setting::), you can edit MIME
message in mh-letter-mode using tm-edit. (*Note (tm_en.info)tm-edit::)

Note: Default setting of mime-setup avoids automatic inserting
      signature when sending a message. Its reason is described at
      *Note (tm_en.info)mime-setup::.



